\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6711,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/20\/eisa-ibn-maryam-benefit-doubt\/","url_meta":{"origin":43818,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Doubts: Jesus gives believers benefit of the doubt","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 20, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cJesus, son of Mary, saw a person he thought was stealing. Jesus said to him: Have you committed theft? The man said: No, by Him besides whom there is no God! Jesus said: I believe in\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17506,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/01\/08\/double-reward-free-marry-slaves\/","url_meta":{"origin":43818,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Slavery: Double reward for freeing, marrying slaves","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 8, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Musa reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIf a man teaches his slave-girl good manners, educates her in the best way, then emancipates her and marries her, he will have a double reward. If he believes in Jesus and then believes in me,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":22075,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/02\/25\/nikah-your-wife-treat-well\/","url_meta":{"origin":43818,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Marriage: She is your wife, if you treat her well","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 25, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Hujr ibn Qays reported: Ali, may Allah be pleased with him, offered a marriage proposal to Fatimah, daughter of the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him. The Prophet said, \u201cShe is yours, if you treat her with the best company.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Kabi\u0304r 3490 Grade: Sahih (authentic)\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":41283,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/09\/29\/treasures-in-heaven\/","url_meta":{"origin":43818,"position":5},"title":"Jesus on Paradise: Store up your treasures in heaven","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 29, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibrahim al-Taymi reported: Jesus, upon him be peace, said, \u201cPlace your treasures in heaven, for the heart of a man is with his treasure.\u201d Source: al-Zuhd li-Ah\u0323mad ibn H\u0323anbal 313 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0625\u0650\u0628\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0627\u0647\u0650\u064a\u0645\u064e \u0627\u0644\u062a\u064e\u0651\u064a\u0652\u0645\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0639\u0650\u064a\u0633\u064e\u0649 \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0633\u064e\u0651\u0644\u064e\u0627\u0645\u064f \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0627\u062c\u0652\u0639\u064e\u0644\u064f\u0648\u0627 \u0643\u064f\u0646\u064f\u0648\u0632\u064e\u0643\u064f\u0645\u0652 \u0641\u0650\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0633\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e\u0627\u0621\u0650 \u0641\u064e\u0625\u0650\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0642\u064e\u0644\u0652